{
  "stem": "20710.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they used to-- whoever they saw on the-- on the-- you know, on the-- the street, they used to pick him up and take him to work.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they picked us up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they took him to another little village, to-- to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we had to stay there all day and work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So what did we do?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They, you know, they-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] know where the trains go by, you know, the-- how you call the iron things that the train-- The rails?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The rails were all, you know, from-- from fighting and bombarding and this, these rails were all, you know, broken and this.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we had to, all day, you know, pick up pieces of-- of iron, with these big screws and take them there to the-- to the rail.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and this was going on all-- all day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then they took him-- took us back to-- to the village, to Bilka.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then next day, we starts running, proceeding to Hanaczow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we came almost close, that I felt that my-- my feet were just not, you know, was [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] like fluid from the blisters coming out.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I couldn't walk anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I said thank god we are here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there was some grass.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Instead of gravel, there was grass.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And while we were proceeding this-- Hanaczow, this village, the people who were-- the-- the Jewish people who were still there, we-- we see they're coming toward us.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they said, don't go there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We are running away because the Ukrainians are after us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they're shooting from all these, you know, surrounding hills.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "(SIGHS)",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we turned around and we went back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was-- it was a-- a tough, tough thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
